column1: Odd columns (1, 3, …) contained Su cultures, even columns contained Lp cultures.
Every other row was initiated with increasingly diluted precultures from the species, from A to O: ['1/25', '1/50', '1/100', '1/200', '1/400', '1/800', '1/1600', '1/3200']
Every 2 columns were filled with media of increasingly high pH: [ 1.11,  1.71,  2.53,  3.28,  4.16,  5.46,  6.92,  7.8 ,  8.44,  8.99,  9.88, 10.56], e.g. cols 3-4 were of pH 1.71
